Execute (View Single-Quote Mark):
  let g:markbar_peekaboo_marks_to_display = '''ABC'
  edit! 10lines.txt
  normal! gg05l
  let cur_pos = getcurpos()
  normal! 'B
  normal '
Expect:
  " Press ? for help
  ['']: (l: 1, c: 5) Last Jump
    ~
    first line
    second line

  ['A]: 10lines.txt [l: 1, c: 5]
    ~
    first line
    second line

  ['B]: 10lines.txt [l: 5, c: 0]
